               <msContents>
                  <summary>Sword of the Trinity, ሠይፈ፡ ሥላሴ፡, Bandlet of Righteousness</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="12v" facs="007">Fols 1r–12v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2295Sayfam">Sayfa malakot</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ቀዳማዊ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ትማልም፡ ወማዕከላዊ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ዮም፡ ወደኃራዊ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ጌሠም፡ ብሉየ፡ መዋዕል፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ዓም፡ ገባሬ፡ ኩሉ፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ድካም፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="13r" to="42r" facs="019">Fols 13r–42r</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1758Lefafa">Lǝfāfa ṣǝdq</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ልፋፈ፡ ጽድቅ፡ በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ድኅነተ፡ ነፍስ፡ ወመጽሐፈ፡ ሕይወት፡ ልፋፈ፡ ጽድቅ፡ ዘወሐባ፡ አብ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ እምቅድመ፡ ይትወለድ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ እምኔሃ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
